docs.text: ZIPING MA I am Ziping Ma (马子平), a first-year M.S. student of Peking University. I have joined the Communication and Information Security Laboratory, under the supervision of Prof. Yuesheng Zhu. My current research interests include data hiding, image generation, and deep learning.
